Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.85,0:00:13.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.05,0:00:14.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.89,0:00:17.18,Main,,0,0,0,,M-Mayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.02,0:00:19.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Looks like mommy's mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.85,0:00:20.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.69,0:00:23.77,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? Are you okay, Iona?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.77,0:00:25.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I'm fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.36,0:00:27.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu can't kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.74,0:00:32.28,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm Mayu's friend, and Mayu's child.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.28,0:00:33.49,Main,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.49,0:00:35.33,Main,,0,0,0,,...I'm also Mayu herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.33,0:00:36.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.12,0:00:37.16,Main,,0,0,0,,...herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.16,0:00:40.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Urith loves me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.50,0:00:42.67,Main,,0,0,0,,That girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.67,0:00:45.92,Main,,0,0,0,,...was raised alone since she was born...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.92,0:00:47.71,Main,,0,0,0,,...without knowing the outside world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.78,0:01:12.28,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Taken and granted,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.28,0:01:16.28,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ideals are repetitious games that slip through{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.28,0:01:19.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My daily life is so shot with holes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.00,0:01:21.87,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that I can barely stand{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.87,0:01:23.17,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Empty theories without conclusions{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.17,0:01:27.38,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dance steps along invisible rules{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.38,0:01:32.38,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The final bell holding together{\i0}\N{\i1}the crumbling day rings{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.38,0:01:36.81,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the scene I imagine{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.81,0:01:39.43,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you're there{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.43,0:01:42.23,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}with a smile{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.23,0:01:47.73,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No forgiveness? No desires?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.73,0:01:51.19,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And still{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.82,0:01:56.03,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We cry "OPEN"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.03,0:02:00.33,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A future to get back and a world to destroy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.33,0:02:02.75,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A wish to open. GOT IT?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.75,0:02:04.42,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now cross{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.42,0:02:07.17,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wish you don't cry{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.17,0:02:14.13,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The future of light and dark,{\i0}\N{\i1}let's believe in the "future"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.13,0:02:20.64,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so that they overlap to gain color again{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.56,0:02:26.15,Main,,0,0,0,,The girl was all alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.15,0:02:29.36,Main,,0,0,0,,...without knowing what being "alone" meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.66,0:02:44.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Every so often, something came\Nand did something to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.21,0:02:46.96,Main,,0,0,0,,She didn't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.96,0:02:51.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Who she was, and why she was there...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.01,0:02:55.72,Main,,0,0,0,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.72,0:02:57.89,Main,,0,0,0,,...was her everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.89,0:02:59.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Her world...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.76,0:03:03.31,Main,,0,0,0,,"Friend"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.31,0:03:06.44,Main,,0,0,0,,She then noticed things\Nbeing placed around her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:12.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Periodically, something would\Ncome by to bring things to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.45,0:03:18.70,Main,,0,0,0,,She had no idea why.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.70,0:03:22.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe there was pity towards the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.08,0:03:24.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Or, maybe it was just a whim.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.26,0:03:37.34,Main,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.34,0:03:39.76,Main,,0,0,0,,...is ...this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.51,0:03:46.35,Main,,0,0,0,,She then found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.35,0:03:52.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Beyond that window, there's a world\Noutside that she's not aware of.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:04:01.37,Main,,0,0,0,,That there are many girls\Nout there that look like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.87,0:04:03.53,Main,,0,0,0,,"...a lot of friends..."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.87,0:04:08.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Frie... nd...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.41,0:04:09.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Their wish... came true...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.33,0:04:11.67,Main,,0,0,0,,"...and everyone lived happily ever after"\NTheir wish... came true...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.04,0:04:14.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.80,0:04:16.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Then one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.18,0:04:25.35,Main,,0,0,0,,She understood that it was\Nsome sort of plaything...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.35,0:04:28.10,Main,,0,0,0,,...and that it couldn't be played by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.82,0:04:38.24,Main,,0,0,0,,She then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.01,0:05:08.27,Main,,0,0,0,,...created friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.23,0:05:10.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Friends...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.73,0:05:17.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Imaginary friends that were only\Nin her mind and only she could see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.40,0:05:21.70,Main,,0,0,0,,You're the Girl of Light, the good girl, Shiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.70,0:05:25.82,Main,,0,0,0,,You're the Girl of Dark, the bad girl, Kuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:28.66,Main,,0,0,0,,We're friends from today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.66,0:05:30.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup, nice to meet you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.62,0:05:33.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure, I'll be your friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.17,0:05:39.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Shiro's going to summon Tlet...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.84,0:05:42.01,Main,,0,0,0,,That won't work, Shiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.01,0:05:44.39,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll stop that with Vimana...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.39,0:05:47.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Aah... no...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:48.93,Main,,0,0,0,,It's Kuro's turn next...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.93,0:05:50.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Here I go... Attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.85,0:05:53.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Yikes, she got me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.69,0:05:57.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, it's your turn, Shiro. Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.61,0:06:00.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup, Shiro will do her best...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.19,0:06:03.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Next, she started a certain game.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.90,0:06:05.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Outside world...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.91,0:06:07.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.41,0:06:12.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Shiro and Kuro are going to bring\Ngirls from the outside world here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:16.38,Main,,0,0,0,,You'll tell them that if they win the game,\Ntheir wish will come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.38,0:06:18.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Then what...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.21,0:06:20.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Shiro and Kuro are going to play WIXOSS,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.88,0:06:24.26,Main,,0,0,0,,and whoever wins will be granted\Nthe wish of the girl they brought.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.26,0:06:27.80,Main,,0,0,0,,What's going to happen to that girl...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.80,0:06:30.39,Main,,0,0,0,,She'll be sealed away in the world of cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.39,0:06:34.48,Main,,0,0,0,,For her to escape from there,\Nshe'll have to bring another girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.48,0:06:36.86,Main,,0,0,0,,What about the girl who loses...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.86,0:06:39.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Her wish won't come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.52,0:06:41.78,Main,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.78,0:06:44.36,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.36,0:06:47.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Her wish will be reversed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.03,0:06:48.16,Main,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.16,0:06:50.08,Main,,0,0,0,,...a Selector battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.08,0:06:51.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:58.67,Main,,0,0,0,,But, isn't that mean...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.67,0:06:59.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.96,0:07:03.80,Main,,0,0,0,,That girl can choose whether\Nshe wants to play or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.80,0:07:05.93,Main,,0,0,0,,She doesn't have to play if she doesn't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.93,0:07:08.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm, that sounds fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.14,0:07:10.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Right? Now, let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:13.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup, Shiro will do it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.18,0:07:15.64,Main,,0,0,0,,And so, it began...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.85,0:07:20.94,Main,,0,0,0,,It's Shiro's turn... Here I go, Kuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.94,0:07:23.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Rococo Boundary...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.69,0:07:26.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow, that's great, Shiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.53,0:07:29.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Shiro-{\i1}chan{\i0}, please do your best for me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.58,0:07:34.45,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to become a florist...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:36.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup, Shiro will do her best...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.79,0:07:39.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, it's your turn, Kuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.00,0:07:43.67,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't lose to you yet, Shiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.67,0:07:47.18,Main,,0,0,0,,I hope Kuro-{\i1}chan {\i0}wins so that\NI can become a princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.18,0:07:49.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Dark Matter...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.39,0:07:51.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay! Kuro wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.55,0:07:53.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Kuro-{\i1}chan{\i0}, thank you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:56.18,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.39,0:07:59.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.35,0:08:02.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Now that you lost,\Nyour dream will be reversed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.86,0:08:05.69,Main,,0,0,0,,You won't become a florist.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.44,0:08:09.11,Main,,0,0,0,,And, that's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.11,0:08:13.99,Main,,0,0,0,,You will never be able to\Nsmell or see flowers anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.99,0:08:16.79,Main,,0,0,0,,You'll go to a world where flowers don't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.00,0:08:22.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Now I can become a princess...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:23.67,Main,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:30.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Kuro will fulfill your dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.18,0:08:34.68,Main,,0,0,0,,If you want to escape,\Nbring a girl to replace you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:38.52,Main,,0,0,0,,And so, the world she bore...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.52,0:08:41.69,Main,,0,0,0,,...began to bear bright colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.69,0:08:43.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Within the imaginary world...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.65,0:08:45.82,Main,,0,0,0,,...the girls' laughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.82,0:08:47.24,Main,,0,0,0,,...their cries...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.24,0:08:48.95,Main,,0,0,0,,...their screams...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.95,0:08:51.20,Main,,0,0,0,,...resonated over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.45,0:08:53.83,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.83,0:08:57.29,Main,,0,0,0,,...the more her imaginary\Nworld gained reality...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.29,0:09:00.96,Main,,0,0,0,,...the more she knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.96,0:09:03.46,Main,,0,0,0,,...where she was.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.46,0:09:08.38,Main,,0,0,0,,A world of truth where\Nthere are no colors or voices...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.18,0:09:14.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Say, Shiro, Kuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.05,0:09:16.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Isn't it strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.18,0:09:21.27,Main,,0,0,0,,You're my friends,\Nbut I'm the only one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.27,0:09:24.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Not only can't I wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.69,0:09:28.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't even see what a florist is like.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:32.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Say, Mayu...? What is Mayu's wish...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.95,0:09:35.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Shiro and Kuro will fulfill your wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:39.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Really? You're both so kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.00,0:09:45.34,Main,,0,0,0,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.34,0:09:46.84,Main,,0,0,0,,...wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.84,0:09:58.01,Main,,0,0,0,,That girl is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.01,0:10:01.85,Main,,0,0,0,,This is... me, Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.85,0:10:03.85,Main,,0,0,0,,...and Mayu's story.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.19,0:10:09.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Then... my meeting with Mayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:11.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.19,0:10:14.20,Main,,0,0,0,,She's still wishing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.20,0:10:17.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Even now, in that very room...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.16,0:10:20.45,Main,,0,0,0,,...she's wishing all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.91,0:10:24.25,Main,,0,0,0,,And I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.38,0:10:27.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.67,0:10:30.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.50,0:10:32.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-Where am I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.84,0:10:38.85,Main,,0,0,0,,It was then I understood everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.47,0:10:44.14,Main,,0,0,0,,So... Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:52.90,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm Kuro. I'll fulfill your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.70,0:10:57.03,Main,,0,0,0,,That was Mayu's wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.03,0:10:59.37,Main,,0,0,0,,...that she yearns for from that room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.37,0:11:03.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Strongly... Sharply... Earnestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.08,0:11:05.71,Main,,0,0,0,,What is Mayu-{\i1}san{\i0}'s wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.71,0:11:07.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.34,0:11:13.34,Main,,0,0,0,,To those who live in the outside world,\Nwho are allowed to have wishes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.34,0:11:17.59,Main,,0,0,0,,To all the girls who are allowed to select...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.80,0:11:22.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Revenge...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.18,0:11:25.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Revenge...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:35.36,Main,,0,0,0,,The other girls Mayu bore became LRIGs, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.36,0:11:38.62,Main,,0,0,0,,...I continued my battles against them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.82,0:11:42.74,Main,,0,0,0,,What happened to the LRIGs who lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.74,0:11:48.04,Main,,0,0,0,,They disappeared and their\NSelectors replaced them as LRIGs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.04,0:11:50.71,Main,,0,0,0,,The only LRIGs Mayu bore who are still alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.71,0:11:52.09,Main,,0,0,0,,...are me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.09,0:11:53.38,Main,,0,0,0,,...and Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.17,0:11:58.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Winning led me to become a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.43,0:12:00.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:02.89,Main,,0,0,0,,...an LRIG came to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.02,0:12:08.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I continued to battle to\Nbecome an LRIG again...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.23,0:12:12.77,Main,,0,0,0,,...then a Selector, then an LRIG again,\Nand continued my life as such.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.77,0:12:14.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.23,0:12:15.99,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought I told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.99,0:12:18.99,Main,,0,0,0,,...that's just what I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.99,0:12:19.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Kuro...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.99,0:12:22.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, you're Kuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.66,0:12:24.28,Main,,0,0,0,,The bad girl, Kuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.28,0:12:29.16,Main,,0,0,0,,You battle for eternity to bring misery to all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.16,0:12:32.88,Main,,0,0,0,,That's your fate as the Girl of Dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.42,0:12:37.59,Main,,0,0,0,,After repeating myself between\Nbeing an LRIG and Selector...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.59,0:12:40.63,Main,,0,0,0,,...I became Urazoe Iona, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.85,0:12:46.35,Main,,0,0,0,,...Urith came to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.35,0:12:50.27,Main,,0,0,0,,...in the form from back when I was called Kuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.27,0:12:52.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Urith...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.31,0:12:55.86,Main,,0,0,0,,But, why the change in form?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.86,0:12:57.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Playing with dolls...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.19,0:13:00.32,Main,,0,0,0,,We're just dolls...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.32,0:13:02.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Guess everyone was just being played with...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.45,0:13:04.62,Main,,0,0,0,,But, you're friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.62,0:13:08.79,Main,,0,0,0,,You said that you and Tama are\NMayu's friends, and Mayu herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.79,0:13:10.50,Main,,0,0,0,,That makes no difference...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.50,0:13:12.21,Main,,0,0,0,,...to her at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.21,0:13:13.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't care...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.92,0:13:18.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if it was someone's wish, or even if\Nthis is some game, I was able to meet Urith...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.42,0:13:20.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I was able to meet Urith!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.92,0:13:22.59,Main,,0,0,0,,She's lost it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.59,0:13:24.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Battling is my fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.85,0:13:29.14,Main,,0,0,0,,But, I started to become serious\Nas the battles continued.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.14,0:13:30.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:33.36,Main,,0,0,0,,It was the first time I felt like I was alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.36,0:13:36.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I felt my own soul and my own body.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.69,0:13:40.70,Main,,0,0,0,,I felt... that I really am alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.74,0:13:47.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Since then, I've sought to become stronger\Nby looking for the greatest of Selectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.62,0:13:51.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Then I met you, Ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:55.13,Main,,0,0,0,,And... You were there, Shiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.13,0:13:59.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I lost to Ru, and my wish came true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.34,0:14:01.22,Main,,0,0,0,,...you didn't battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.22,0:14:03.09,Main,,0,0,0,,I couldn't forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.68,0:14:08.72,Main,,0,0,0,,You're supposed to be the same as me,\Nand yet you cuddled with simpletons...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.72,0:14:11.64,Main,,0,0,0,,That seemed nonsensical to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.69,0:14:16.90,Main,,0,0,0,,But then, Ru entered me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.90,0:14:21.53,Main,,0,0,0,,It felt nice and warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.28,0:14:27.08,Main,,0,0,0,,So that's what you felt, wasn't it, Tama?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.08,0:14:28.95,Main,,0,0,0,,You and Ru's strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.95,0:14:31.75,Main,,0,0,0,,...comes from bonding with\Nothers and feeling empathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.75,0:14:36.54,Main,,0,0,0,,You experienced that and felt that,\Nso you were able to change, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.54,0:14:40.34,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why you refused to\Ndo the battles you loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:46.30,Main,,0,0,0,,You have something more\Nimportant than battling now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.30,0:14:49.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama don't need to battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.81,0:14:52.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I like Ru more than battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.85,0:14:55.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.02,0:14:56.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I like Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.56,0:14:58.06,Main,,0,0,0,,I like Hitoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.06,0:14:59.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I like Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.57,0:15:01.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I like everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.36,0:15:02.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.40,0:15:06.07,Main,,0,0,0,,I want Mayu to become\Nfriends with everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.07,0:15:10.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Then she'll stop doing this!\NNo one has to battle anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:14.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama? Did you get your memory back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.00,0:15:14.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.83,0:15:15.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.71,0:15:19.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu was lonely being all by herself...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.88,0:15:22.84,Main,,0,0,0,,But, Tama forgot all about Mayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.84,0:15:28.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama, you said that you felt you could\Nreturn all the girls back from LRIGs, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.93,0:15:31.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Yup, but I'm not too sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.85,0:15:35.60,Main,,0,0,0,,You said that because you're Mayu's light.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.60,0:15:37.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu-{\i1}san{\i0}'s light?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.81,0:15:41.65,Main,,0,0,0,,You and I changed being\Nwith Ru and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.65,0:15:42.44,Main,,0,0,0,,If so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.44,0:15:45.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu can become friends\Nwith Ru and everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.36,0:15:49.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. Let's both show her the feelings we hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.20,0:15:51.08,Main,,0,0,0,,If that happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.08,0:15:56.96,Main,,0,0,0,,...then we can end Selector battles, and save\Nall the girls who turned into LRIGs, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.88,0:16:01.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona... Tama...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.54,0:16:03.59,Main,,0,0,0,,You can hear us, right, Mayu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.59,0:16:05.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Playtime is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.63,0:16:09.59,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll bring you out from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.18,0:16:13.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.93,0:16:16.02,Main,,0,0,0,,What's with those girls?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.02,0:16:18.02,Main,,0,0,0,,No...! So scary...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.02,0:16:20.61,Main,,0,0,0,,To save everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.61,0:16:22.07,Main,,0,0,0,,...we need to defeat Urith!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.07,0:16:26.24,Main,,0,0,0,,If we can beat her,\Nwe'll finally be able to save Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.24,0:16:30.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Then Tama-{\i1}chan {\i0}and Iona-{\i1}san{\i0}\Ncan be together again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.58,0:16:35.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm tired of all this nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.66,0:16:39.42,Main,,0,0,0,,It's supposed to be my turn next, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.42,0:16:43.34,Main,,0,0,0,,This is great, seeing everyone\Nshining brilliantly with hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.34,0:16:44.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't dump me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:48.72,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll crush that brilliance of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.72,0:16:51.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but Tama is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.26,0:16:55.31,Main,,0,0,0,,I need to break even more girls using her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.31,0:16:56.47,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.47,0:17:00.60,Main,,0,0,0,,All until my very kind Tama-{\i1}chan{\i0}'s\Nheart is broken to pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.60,0:17:03.31,Main,,0,0,0,,I... I won't let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.31,0:17:06.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona is at Level 5, higher\Nthan Tama who's at Level 4!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.61,0:17:10.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Well... how's this then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.11,0:17:11.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.07,0:17:18.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll stain that beautiful\Nbody of yours in darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.67,0:17:27.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama! Tama...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.42,0:17:28.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Music to my ears...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.88,0:17:30.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Impossible! Urith is entering Tama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.92,0:17:34.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Aah... So beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.05,0:17:36.43,Main,,0,0,0,,No! No! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.43,0:17:37.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Why her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.85,0:17:40.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Urith... is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.85,0:17:44.27,Main,,0,0,0,,R-Ru... Iona... What's happening...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.27,0:17:47.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Something is... entering Tama...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.36,0:17:49.53,Main,,0,0,0,,No... I don't want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.53,0:17:51.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Help... Ru...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.11,0:17:52.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.33,0:17:56.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.58,0:17:58.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.75,0:18:03.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Again-lun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.48,0:18:27.61,Main,,0,0,0,,It... can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.61,0:18:29.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Fafnir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.45,0:18:37.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.20,0:18:39.04,Main,,0,0,0,,End Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.71,0:18:52.13,Main,,0,0,0,,T-Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.13,0:18:53.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Hardcore...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.26,0:18:56.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop! Stop, Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.14,0:19:04.31,Main,,0,0,0,,No...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.98,0:19:10.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.16,0:19:22.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.67,0:19:29.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.85,0:19:41.47,Main,,0,0,0,,No... Tama did...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.47,0:19:44.31,Main,,0,0,0,,N-No! Tama, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.31,0:19:46.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.10,0:19:48.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.15,0:19:51.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Ionaaa...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.42,0:20:12.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Too bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.76,0:20:15.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.81,0:20:26.60,Main,,0,0,0,,That was fun... you hopeless scum.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.60,0:20:28.27,Main,,0,0,0,,W-Wait... Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.27,0:20:29.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe! Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.44,0:20:31.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki... Ruko...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.24,0:20:44.62,Main,,0,0,0,,That felt great.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.62,0:20:45.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Urith...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.91,0:20:47.58,Main,,0,0,0,,What is it, Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.58,0:20:51.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Am I... unsightly?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.08,0:20:52.21,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.25,0:20:56.51,Main,,0,0,0,,You're beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.51,0:20:59.59,Main,,0,0,0,,You haven't changed ever\Nsince I've longed for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.59,0:21:03.26,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll be together, forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.26,0:21:06.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's have fun together...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.47,0:21:11.10,Main,,0,0,0,,...with all the girls' wishes in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.65,0:21:20.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Urith...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.40,0:21:22.20,Main,,0,0,0,,...you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.64,0:21:52.39,Main,,0,0,0,,A... ki... ra...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.48,0:22:01.99,Main,,0,0,0,,"This World is My Property"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.33,0:22:09.79,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Life...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.79,0:22:15.25,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A city of mazes with no exit{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.25,0:22:19.76,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the sound of bells ringing{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.76,0:22:21.38,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I do...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.38,0:22:26.97,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Leave the "now" handed to me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.97,0:22:31.68,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}as I begin to walk in the morning{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.68,0:22:37.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In a world where light and dark intersect{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.15,0:22:43.32,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}catharsis begins to awake{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.32,0:22:48.41,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I swore in my shaking heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.41,0:22:58.59,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that I won't lose anyone anymore...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.17,0:23:05.22,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if my tears flow tomorrow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.22,0:23:11.93,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll run through the wind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.93,0:23:16.98,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Release myself towards the future I selected{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.98,0:23:19.61,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to regain it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.61,0:23:26.74,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't give up on my wish{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.91,0:23:34.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I sense an unusual, evildoer's aura...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.91,0:23:35.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.66,0:23:37.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Such evil...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.21,0:23:38.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm evil?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.54,0:23:40.46,Main,,0,0,0,,...your time of punishment will come!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.46,0:23:44.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Justice will prevail!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.80,0:23:46.84,Main,,0,0,0,,"That Abrupt Separation"\NThat Abrupt Separation.
